{"lemma": "جُنْدُبٌ", "slug": "جُنْدُبٌ", "root": "ج.ن.د.ب", "root_slug": "ج-ن-د-ب", "root_link": "/words/roots/ج-ن-د-ب", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 1, "pos_tags": ["noun"], "has_etymology": true, "sense_count": 1}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n5195", "n6462"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8F%D9%86%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8F%D8%A8%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "grasshopper", "fa": "ملخ", "ur": "ٹڈی", "tr": "çekirge", "id": "belalang", "bn": "ট্যাঁচা", "es": "saltamontes", "fr": "sauterelle", "de": "Heuschrecke", "ru": "сверчок", "zh": "蝗虫"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "noun", "gloss": "grasshopper"}]}, "etymology": {"source": "wiktextract", "text": "Compare جَدْجَد (jadjad)."}, "ipa": ["/d͡ʒun.dub/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n5195", "headword_ar": "جُنْدَبٌ", "root": "jdb", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "junodubN", "text_ar": "جُنْدُبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, &c.) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jinodabN", "text_ar": "جِنْدَبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "dirohamN", "text_ar": "دِرْهَمٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Sb, M, K,) the last of which is of weakest authority, because of a rare measure, whereof it has been said that there are only four examples: (TA:) in all of them the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "n", "text_ar": "ن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is said by some to be radical; but others, with more reason, hold it to be augmentative: (MF:) Sb says that it is augmentative: (S:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A species of locust,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "well known:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) or the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "male locust:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "small locust:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, accord. to Seer,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SadFY", "text_ar": "صَدًى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a kind of cricket"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that creaks by night, and hops and flies:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[but see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SadFY", "text_ar": "صَدًى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":] or, accord. to the M, it is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "smaller than the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SdY", "text_ar": "صدى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and is found in the deserts:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "janaAdibu", "text_ar": "جَنَادِبُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sr~", "text_ar": "صرّ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aljndb", "text_ar": "الجندب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sar~a Aljunodabu", "text_ar": "صَرَّ الجُنْدَبُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jndb", "text_ar": "جندب"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "creaked"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] is a saying of the Arabs, used as a proverb; alluding to a difficult affair by which a person is troubled in mind; originating from the fact that the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jndb", "text_ar": "جندب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", when its feet are scorched by the heated ground, does not keep them steadily upon it, and a creaking sound is consequently heard, produced by its legs. (TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^um~u junodabK", "text_ar": "اُمُّ جُنْدَبٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sand;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "because the locust [or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jndb", "text_ar": "جندب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] deposits its eggs therein: and the walker therein falls into evil [or encounters difficulty]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence it signifies also]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Misfortune:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, K:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "perfidy,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "faithlessness,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "treachery:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wrong,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "injury:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, K:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "evil conduct,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ill treatment."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waqaEa fulaAnN fiY", "text_ar": "وَقَعَ فُلَانٌ فِى"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^um~i junodabK", "text_ar": "اُمِّ جُنْدَبٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one fell into misfortune:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "into perfidy."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waqaEuwA fiY A^um~i junodabK", "text_ar": "وَقَعُوا فِى اُمِّ جُنْدَبٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They suffered wrong,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "injury."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AZ, S, K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waqaEa Alqawomu junodabK", "text_ar": "وَقَعَ القَوْمُ جُنْدَبٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The people,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "company of men, committed wrong,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "injury, and slew him who was not a slayer:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) [as though they came with violence upon sand in which eggs of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jndb", "text_ar": "جندب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "were deposited, and so destroyed the eggs, which had occasioned them no harm.] And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rakiba A^um~a junodabK", "text_ar": "رَكِبَ اُمَّ جُنْدَبٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He committed wrong,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "injury."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["Sb", "M", "K", "TA", "MF", "S"]}, {"entry_id": "n6462", "headword_ar": "جُنْدَبٌ", "root": "jndb", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "junodubN", "text_ar": "جُنْدُبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "janodabN", "text_ar": "جَنْدَبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": see art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jdb", "text_ar": "جدب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": []}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}